# 📄 Local PDF Chatbot

An AI-powered chatbot that lets users chat with PDF documents.

## 🚀 Features

- Upload any PDF
- Ask questions about the document
- Local AI processing using Ollama
- No API cost
- Private document processing

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- LangChain
- Ollama
- Llama 3.1
- Nomic Embeddings

## Architecture

PDF  
↓  
Document Chunking  
↓  
Embeddings  
↓  
Vector Search  
↓  
Local LLM  
↓  
Answer

